Actions.Text: REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS

Title: Establishes a credit against the franchise tax on business corporations for the cost of replacing concord grapevines by a farm
Summary: Establishes a credit against the franchise tax on business corporations for the cost of replacing concord grapevines by a farm.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the tax law, in relation to establishing a grapevine replacement franchise tax on business corporations credit
